title: 30 Minute Heart Pumping Elliptical HIIT Workout
description:
Hop on your elliptical and let’s get some heart-pumping cardio in today with this 30 Minute Elliptical HIIT Workout! Join coach Sydney, as she invites you to push your pace and resistance through a variety of intervals. Are you up for the challenge? 

30 Minute Heart Pumping Elliptical HIIT Workout
Workout Length: 30-Minute
Workout Level: Intermediate
Trainer: Sydney Eaton
